And everybody thinks that
there's some kind of door

00:42:24.340 --> 00:42:28.340
that the 40 or 50 food people
like me all walk through

00:42:28.340 --> 00:42:30.530
and we're alone in
this fantastic place

00:42:30.530 --> 00:42:32.120
and there's just vats of caviar.

