stories around food

00:50:05.040 --> 00:50:07.170
rather than divisive
ones about who

00:50:07.170 --> 00:50:09.600
you like to have sex with,
what music do we listen to,

00:50:09.600 --> 00:50:12.340
what kind of god do we believe
in, what language do we speak,

00:50:12.340 --> 00:50:13.760
what color is our skin.

00:50:13.760 --> 00:50:15.180
All that shit's irrelevant.

00:50:15.180 --> 00:50:16.450
This is 2016.

00:50:16.450 --> 00:50:17.951
It's a very, very flat world.

00:50:17.951 --> 00:50:19.700
Let's talk about the
things that unite us,

00:50:19.700 --> 00:50:21.280
not the things that divide us.

